{"tid":2346331,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"popo查身份證","createTime":"2020-12-30T07:36:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-30T09:04:26.000Z","uid":318291,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"204d05a39014028d035ca36b9ea7bf61030f295a","tid":2346331,"uid":318291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T07:36:55.000Z","msg":"尋日黃昏6-7點左右，我喺灣仔A2出口上面、行人天橋下面、灣電對面篤緊手機。突然有三隻popo行埋黎問我做緊乜、攞身份證又要我打開背囊俾佢搜。我話我等緊巴士（其實我係想去法協對出巴士站等車番屋企但又想check下仲有無野買先），俾張證佢哋又打開個袋。好彩裡面無可以俾佢哋屈係攻擊性武器、違反國安法、意圖犯法之類可以被莫須有嘅野。有隻popo抄底我張證資料然後用對講機讀出我身份證編號，跟住片刻之後，好似收到對方回覆。好似係確定唔係要搵嘅人之類嘅感覺，俾番張證我、示意我走得。我稍為追問，佢哋確定無事啦。<br />\n<br />\n其實佢哋會係做緊乜？6點幾喺果個位睇手機係好正常嘅事。你話我遊蕩、叫我早啲番屋企都唔make sense。佢哋特別係想確認我身份證號碼會同對講機另一邊嘅資料配合咁，但會係乜嘢資料？佢哋搵緊定想捉去差館嘅係乜人？<br />\n<br />\n個感覺係不安架、撞邪咁。無情情年尾俾popo睇中要check身份證仲要俾佢摸咁。是咪要求番串佛珠護身好？"},{"pid":"0ce9f753a820db96020ab621d94c3b139db6696b","tid":2346331,"uid":214358,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T07:38:41.000Z","msg":"佢地間唔中係咁發下癲架啦 第一日識佢地？"},{"pid":"0eb5c4829ed916508da70df38a224ff0b9e8c267","tid":2346331,"uid":353080,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T07:39:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"408a0260a84171933b75e67fb15592fea5fd03e4","tid":2346331,"uid":341649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T07:39:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ajUZsV5.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FajUZsV5.gif&h=f6c01475&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n江湖術士係咁"},{"pid":"ef6f76f8aa68a88a281184b43bd7dd692bf7cd57","tid":2346331,"uid":13518,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T07:40:42.000Z","msg":"第一次比佢地查證？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d97df7ebbab17a38dcd42e43a715bb5ac374151a","tid":2346331,"uid":378305,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T07:41:58.000Z","msg":"你有丁丁都可以屈強姦<br />\n<br />\n有西西屈你當街賣淫，任佢up"},{"pid":"1cd26987b36cc22070aa3f4aa1b2f175d4668846","tid":2346331,"uid":318291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef6f76f8aa68a88a281184b43bd7dd692bf7cd57","tid":2346331,"uid":13518,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T07:40:42.000Z","msg":"第一次比佢地查證？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T07:42:07.000Z","msg":"咁就無咗第一次🥺好似俾人強、又無得嗌唔好😭"},{"pid":"443392d3247567494369eba2965dbe5693fc8942","tid":2346331,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T07:42:52.000Z","msg":"每個行街軍裝都要交quota，每日都要搵人check<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"481ced863e42d32fc2baa0e5959ec6d31d7fb5b2","tid":2346331,"uid":51963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T07:44:43.000Z","msg":"今日荃灣, 旺角都見到, 被查既係後生, 便服黑衫黑褲"},{"pid":"128e4da7a0e90d814d898c89616d1c33667552a8","tid":2346331,"uid":318291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"481ced863e42d32fc2baa0e5959ec6d31d7fb5b2","tid":2346331,"uid":51963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T07:44:43.000Z","msg":"今日荃灣, 旺角都見到, 被查既係後生, 便服黑衫黑褲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T07:48:02.000Z","msg":"係喎，屌。我黑衫黑褲，外套灰色反出黎有amber黃，個口罩又係黃色。😭"},{"pid":"dfab27538d52fe17d8ebd3495157456065bc1b26","tid":2346331,"uid":333880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T08:04:37.000Z","msg":"一直都係咁架 無咩特別 D狗要交功課"},{"pid":"906f227ff4b40bc9e4c82992d583449395b71134","tid":2346331,"uid":123696,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T08:16:11.000Z","msg":"佢哋成日都唔跟規則做事<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先你要搞清楚<br />\n截停同搜身係兩樣嘢<br />\n法律上容許佢亂咁喺街截停人 叫人出示身份證<br />\n呢樣你無得同佢嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/tired.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係要搜身或者搜袋嘅話<br />\n警隊條例第54(1)/(2)條要求佢一定要有「合理懷疑」<br />\n理論上你可以問佢：「你有咩合理懷疑？」<img src=\"/assets/faces/catxm/stare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後同佢嘈<br />\n如果佢答唔出/懷疑唔合理<br />\n法律上你可以拒絕佢搜身／搜袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n根據終審法院<em>楊美雲</em>案嘅判辭，如果佢個搜身係唔合法嘅，即使你拒絕搜身，你都唔算係阻差辦公<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/ohyes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過咁 如果你真係拒絕 而佢哋真係入你阻差辦工<br />\n咁附近嘅人證物證就係關鍵<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n閉路電視 路人嘅口供 甚至你部電話嘅錄影錄音都好緊要<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為十個官 九個信警察<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以如果無客觀嘅第三方證供 你一個對<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />對你好不利<br />\n<br />\n所以咁嘅情況你應該儘量引途人注意去保障自己 <br />\n途人可以做證人<br />\n儘量畀壓力佢哋<br />\n事後如果記得佢哋number 仲可以投訴<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有無用都好<br />\n唔好畀佢哋偷雞偷得咁過癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d01a0dabcba75966f1202366be6ca5d4e962a90","tid":2346331,"uid":123696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1cd26987b36cc22070aa3f4aa1b2f175d4668846","tid":2346331,"uid":318291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef6f76f8aa68a88a281184b43bd7dd692bf7cd57","tid":2346331,"uid":13518,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T07:40:42.000Z","msg":"第一次比佢地查證？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T07:42:07.000Z","msg":"咁就無咗第一次🥺好似俾人強、又無得嗌唔好😭"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T08:19:02.000Z","msg":"俾人強一定要吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc8bd3487d94ed9b41ac516f0a040e16ef8f7344","tid":2346331,"uid":626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T08:19:10.000Z","msg":"一般查身份證都係咁, 要交數, 以前都係咁, <br />\n只不過以前係搵可疑人士來查, 而家係搵後生仔查"},{"pid":"5b0cae1b32018ecc058390cf3226dd3f5d620162","tid":2346331,"uid":238214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T08:24:34.000Z","msg":"查下你係咪通緝人士之類"},{"pid":"63c678cb14f97b49eca6238634175fb6f144b2ae","tid":2346331,"uid":218313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T08:27:23.000Z","msg":"佢地專揀後生仔查<br />\n我見過好撚多次<br />\n<br />\n你著黑色衫行過, 9 成會俾狗逗"},{"pid":"418f57aff6de2448ddc55ecbe7f93e8e61d1d590","tid":2346331,"uid":133534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T08:34:57.000Z","msg":"樓主你同自爆acct 無分別喎<br />\n<br />\n有時間地點人物加埋呢個post<br />\n<br />\n係Popo 都知呢個acct 係你啦<br />\n<br />\n你無post過啲乜嘢嘛？<br />\n<br />\n定你借朋友acct 咋？"},{"pid":"f787301930e16a0b4fb1d9feac59f8ee79f8cbbc","tid":2346331,"uid":378305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"63c678cb14f97b49eca6238634175fb6f144b2ae","tid":2346331,"uid":218313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T08:27:23.000Z","msg":"佢地專揀後生仔查<br />\n我見過好撚多次<br />\n<br />\n你著黑色衫行過, 9 成會俾狗逗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T09:04:26.000Z","msg":"其實佢哋知唔知好擾民架？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n為左佢地交差，浪費左我十幾分鐘時間，又無得claim返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過班狗都唔會理解到人類嘅生活模式架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}